data.description: Well maintained home on 1/2 acre lot in the Twin Ponds lake community. Just a short golf cart ride to Buncombe Creek Marina. Large kitchen with tons of cabinets, and an eat at island. Open concept is great for entertaining.  Large master suite with walk in closet, and a soaker tub for relaxing. Large covered patio for grilling, and outdoor entertaining. Whether you’re looking for a vacation home for yourself, investment opportunity, or full time residence this home is ideal. Schedule your showing today!
